          Proof, not <span style="color: hsl(var(--cobalt));">promises</span>.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12 border-t border-foreground/[0.08] pt-14 md:pt-16">
        {testimonials.map((t) => (
